  "detailed_description": "<strong>The Odyssey of the last chance</strong><br><br>Follow the adventures of ILO, a small magician robot sent by humans to a planet of last resort.<br><br>With its pointed hat and Magic Book, Ilo explores a world full of hostile creatures to find the terraforming beacons. It makes its way using “magical” blocks. The powers to fly, stop time or pass through objects are all powers that will help it overcome obstacles and bravely continue its odyssey.<br><br>Magibot combines the principles of a platform game and those of a strategy game. Wisely place the action blocks upstream before taking control of your character.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/690850/extras/6b7221ca3707ffef5d4de6cb2edb9160.poster.avif?t=1750429249\" width=314 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/690850/extras/6b7221ca3707ffef5d4de6cb2edb9160.webm?t=1750429249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/690850/extras/6b7221ca3707ffef5d4de6cb2edb9160.mp4?t=1750429249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unique blend of a platform game and a strategy game<br></li><li>9 magical powers to acquire<br></li><li>40 Highly interactive Levels<br></li><li>2 game modes: Puzzle and Action</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>The Odyssey of the last chance</strong><br><br>Follow the adventures of ILO, a small magician robot sent by humans to a planet of last resort.<br><br>With its pointed hat and Magic Book, Ilo explores a world full of hostile creatures to find the terraforming beacons. It makes its way using “magical” blocks. The powers to fly, stop time or pass through objects are all powers that will help it overcome obstacles and bravely continue its odyssey.<br><br>Magibot combines the principles of a platform game and those of a strategy game. Wisely place the action blocks upstream before taking control of your character.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/690850/extras/6b7221ca3707ffef5d4de6cb2edb9160.poster.avif?t=1750429249\" width=314 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/690850/extras/6b7221ca3707ffef5d4de6cb2edb9160.webm?t=1750429249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/690850/extras/6b7221ca3707ffef5d4de6cb2edb9160.mp4?t=1750429249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unique blend of a platform game and a strategy game<br></li><li>9 magical powers to acquire<br></li><li>40 Highly interactive Levels<br></li><li>2 game modes: Puzzle and Action</li></ul>",
